[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛祖綱目卷第九(日字號)",
        "translation": "Fozu gongmu, vol. 9 (Niji hao)",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a07_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "甲子(周定王十年起)丙子(簡王元年)庚寅(靈王元年)丁巳(景王元年)癸亥(周景王七年止)(辛未)七祖婆須蜜傳法佛陀難提婆須蜜。",
        "translation": "Azi (from the tenth year of King Ding of the Zhou dynasty), Czi (from the first year of King Jian), Ginyin (from the first year of King Ling), Dingsi (from the first year of King Jing), and Caphai (from the seventh year of King Jing of the Zhou dynasty) (Xinwei) The seventh patriarch Vasumitra transmitted the teaching of Buddhanandibhasumitra.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a09_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "北天竺國人。",
        "translation": "He was from northern India.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a12_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "姓頗羅墮。",
        "translation": "His family name was Bālādāyin.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a12_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常服淨衣。",
        "translation": "He always wore pure clothing.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a12_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "執酒器遊行里閈。",
        "translation": "He would carry a wine container and promenade through the city.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a12_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或吟或嘯。",
        "translation": "He would chant or shout.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a13_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人謂之狂。",
        "translation": "People called them crazy.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a13_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及遇彌遮迦。",
        "translation": "Then he met Mītṛkā.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a13_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "宣如來往誌。",
        "translation": "He proclaimed the Tathāgata's Record of Past Activities.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a13_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自省前緣。",
        "translation": "He examined his past connections and left home with his vessel.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a14_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "投器出家。",
        "translation": "He threw himself into the container and left home.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a14_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受法行化。",
        "translation": "He received the teaching and practiced transformation.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a14_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至迦摩羅國。",
        "translation": "He went to Kamala.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a14_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "廣興佛事。",
        "translation": "He gave rise to a wide range of Buddhist services.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a14_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於法座前。",
        "translation": "He was in front of the Dharma throne.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a15_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "忽有一智者。",
        "translation": "Suddenly, there was a wise man.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a15_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自稱我名佛陀難提。",
        "translation": "He called himself Buddhanandi.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a15_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今與師論義。",
        "translation": "I'd like to discuss the meaning with my teacher.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a15_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婆須蜜曰。",
        "translation": "Vasumitra said.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a16_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "仁者論即不義。",
        "translation": "\"A theory by a kind person is not meaningful.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a16_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "義即不論。",
        "translation": "Its meaning is not discussed.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a16_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若擬論義。",
        "translation": "If he intends to discuss the meaning, then he won't be able to discuss the meaning.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a16_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "終非義論。",
        "translation": "It's ultimately not a theory of meaning.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a17_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "難提知婆須蜜義勝。",
        "translation": "Nandimitra knew that Vātsumitra's argument was superior.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a17_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心即欽服曰。",
        "translation": "He was immediately convinced and said.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a17_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我願求道。",
        "translation": "'I want to pursue the path.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a17_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "霑甘露味。",
        "translation": "I'll take the taste of ambrosia.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a18_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婆須蜜遂與剃度。",
        "translation": "Vasumitra then gave him his shaving and tonsure.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a18_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而授具戒。",
        "translation": "He was ordained and given the full set of precepts.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a18_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復告之曰。",
        "translation": "He also told him.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a18_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來正法眼藏。",
        "translation": "\"The Tathāgata is the store of the true eye of the Dharma.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a19_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今付汝。",
        "translation": "I've now entrusted it to you.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a19_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝當護持。",
        "translation": "You must safeguard it.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a19_32",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃說偈曰。",
        "translation": "He then spoke a verse, saying.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a19_33",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心同虗空界。",
        "translation": "\"The mind is the same as the realm of smooth space.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示等虗空法。",
        "translation": "It shows the same level of the dharma of nothingness.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a20_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "證得虗空時。",
        "translation": "When he realizes [the reality of] space, it's like space.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a20_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無是無非法。",
        "translation": "Nothing is non-nonexistent.'",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a20_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "偈已。",
        "translation": "After the verse, he spoke.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a21_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婆須蜜即入慈心三昧。",
        "translation": "Vasumitra then entered the samādhi of compassionate mind.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a21_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時梵王帝釋。",
        "translation": "It was then that Brahmā, King Tissa, and the gods came together.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a21_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及諸天眾俱來。",
        "translation": "Brahmā and the gods all came together.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a21_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作禮而說偈言。",
        "translation": "They paid homage and spoke the verse, saying.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a22_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢劫眾聖祖。",
        "translation": "\"Good eons are full of noble ancestors.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a22_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而當第七位。",
        "translation": "They'll be the seventh in line.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a22_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尊者哀念我。",
        "translation": "Venerable Sir, please take pity on me.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a22_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "請為宣佛地。",
        "translation": "Please proclaim the buddha-stage for me!",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a23_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婆須蜜從三昧起。",
        "translation": "Vasumitra rose from his samādhi.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a23_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示眾曰。",
        "translation": "He showed the crowd.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a23_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我所得法。",
        "translation": "\"I've attained the Dharma.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a23_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而非有故。",
        "translation": "It's not existent.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a24_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若識佛地離有無故。",
        "translation": "If I know the Buddha-stage, it's because I'm free of existence and nonexistence.'",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a24_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "語已。",
        "translation": "After he spoke, he returned into samādhi.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a24_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "還入三昧。",
        "translation": "He returned to samādhi.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574a24_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示涅槃相。",
        "translation": "He showed them the characteristics of nirvāṇa.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b01_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "難提即於本座。",
        "translation": "Nandika then took his seat.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b01_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "起七寶塔。",
        "translation": "He raised a stūpa of seven jewels.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b01_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以葬全身。",
        "translation": "He buried his entire body in it.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b01_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當此土周定王十七年辛未歲也。",
        "translation": "It was during the seventeenth year of King Ding of the Zhou dynasty's reign in this land, in the year Xinwei.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b01_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "(庚戌)震旦國孔丘示生",
        "translation": "(Gensho) Kong Qiu of Asunderland was shown birth.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "商帝乙之子。",
        "translation": "He was the son of Shangdi Yi.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b04_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "微子。",
        "translation": "Weizi.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b04_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "始封於宋。",
        "translation": "He was first feuded at Song.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b04_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十三世孔防叔。",
        "translation": "The 13th generation was Kong Fansu.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b04_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "徙居於魯國陬邑平鄉。",
        "translation": "He migrated to Pingxiang, a town in the Ru region.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b04_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "防叔子伯夏。",
        "translation": "Uncle Fang's son Bo Xia.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b05_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "伯夏子叔梁紇。",
        "translation": "Bo Xia's son Shouliang was an outsider.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b05_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先娶鄒氏女。",
        "translation": "He first married a daughter of the Zou family.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b05_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生子孟皮。",
        "translation": "He had a son, Meng Pi.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b06_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不才。",
        "translation": "He was not talented.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b06_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後娶顏氏女名徵。",
        "translation": "He later married a daughter of the Yan family named Zheng.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b06_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "在禱於尼丘山。",
        "translation": "He prayed on Mount Niqiu.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b06_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而生孔子。",
        "translation": "She gave birth to Confucius.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b07_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遂名丘。",
        "translation": "He was then named Qiu.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b07_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "字仲尼。",
        "translation": "His name was Zhonni.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b07_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誕之夕。",
        "translation": "On the eve of his birth.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b07_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二龍遶室。",
        "translation": "Two dragons surrounded his room.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b07_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五老降庭。",
        "translation": "The five old men descended into the courtyard.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b07_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "顏氏之房。",
        "translation": "In the room of the Yan family, he heard the music of Jun Tian.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b08_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞鈞天之樂。",
        "translation": "He heard the music of Jun Tian.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b08_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身長九尺六寸。",
        "translation": "His body is 9 feet, 6 inches long.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b08_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "腰帶十圍。",
        "translation": "His waistband is ten circumferences long.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b08_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "垂手過膝。",
        "translation": "He hangs his arms above his knees.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b09_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "月角日準。",
        "translation": "The moon is angled, the sun is pointed, and the river's eye and mouth are at the ocean.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b09_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "河目海口。",
        "translation": "His eyes are like those of a river and his mouth like the ocean.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b09_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "龍顏方顙鳳顒。",
        "translation": "He has a dragon's face, a squared-off profile, and a phoenix's chin.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b09_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "燕頷。",
        "translation": "He has a swallowed jaw.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b09_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虬髭虎視。",
        "translation": "He has a dragon's moustache and a tiger's gaze.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b10_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眉有十二采。",
        "translation": "His eyebrows have twelve features, and his eyes have sixty-four principles.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b10_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "目有六十四理。",
        "translation": "His eyes had sixty-four perceptions.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b10_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時周靈王二十一年十一月四日。",
        "translation": "It was the fourth day of the eleventh month in the twenty-first year of King Ling of the Zhou.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b10_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "魯襄公二十二年也。",
        "translation": "It was also the twenty-second year of Duke Xiang of Lu.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b11_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋迦會中。",
        "translation": "It was during the Śākyamuni assembly.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b11_32",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "孔子為儒童菩薩。",
        "translation": "Confucius was Rudolph the Bodhisattva.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b12_33",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "顏回為月光菩薩。",
        "translation": "Yan Hui was the Moonlight Bodhisattva.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b12_34",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經云。",
        "translation": "The scripture says.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b12_35",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "閻浮界內。",
        "translation": "\"Within the Jambudvīpa realm.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b12_36",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有震旦國。",
        "translation": "There's the country of AURORA.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b13_37",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我遣三聖。",
        "translation": "I sent three sages.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b13_38",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "在中化導。",
        "translation": "They're here to guide and transform it.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b13_39",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人民慈哀。",
        "translation": "The people are kind and compassionate.",
        "source": "X85n1594_009:0574b13_40",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
